text: Antillophos dedonderi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Nassariidae, the true whelks. ==References== * Fraussen K. & Poppe G.T. (2005) Revision of Phos and Antillophos (Buccinidae) from the Central Philippines. Visaya 1(5): 76-115 ==External links== * Category:Nassariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2005
title: Antillophos dedonderi
